Description:
Fully renovated 3 bedroom home including bungalow and various sheds
This perfectly presented property sure does offer substantial value on the market today. Overloaded with so many extras, it is well placed to accommodate growing families, investors and first home buyers.
The main home offers 3 bedrooms, open plan kitchen/meals/family room, and a secondary multipurpose room.
All the wet areas including the stylish kitchen, bathroom and laundry have been fully renovated.
Great sized bedrooms as well as heating and cooling provided.
Restumping, new flooring and paintwork complement the whole home.
Outside is a fully self-contained bungalow to house the teenager or grand parent of the home, or utilise and take advantage of it as a rental. Sited on a huge (approx.) 1000m2 plus block with various carports, caravan port and huge 6m x 9m shed with concrete floor, power and solar panels that run the home.
Neighbouring crown land and just minutes to Bendigo Central, Bendigo Health and Lake Weeroona. You will not be disappointed.
Insights: 71 Prouses Road, North Bendigo VIC 3550 was last sold in 2020 and 69 other 3 bedroom house in North Bendigo have recently been sold.

Description:
INSTANT LIFESTYLE APPEAL IN A LOW RISE COMPLEX
EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST CLOSING 26 October 2020 AT 5PM UNLESS SOLD PRIOR
DESIGNED TO MAXIMISE NATURAL LIGHT, this sophisticated apartment exemplifies easy contemporary living. Ideally positioned to capture the Northerly aspect. This stylish, boutique  apartment complex is in the heart of South Yarra and offers everything you've been looking for.
SPACIOUS ONE BEDROOM that offers high quality fixtures and fittings.
Delightful open plan that is sun drenched and opens onto a Juliet  balcony.
Stylish spacious kitchen with stone bench tops, plenty of cupboards,electric cooktop and dishwasher.
Spacious bedroom with great outlook and mirrored built-in-robes.
Charming central bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles, full size bathtub and European style laundry facilities.
SPECIAL FEATURES INCLUDES, reverse cycle heating and cooling in the living room, Lift access, Secure car parking. Building facilities include indoor swimming pool, steam room, gymnasium and an inviting sitting room in the foyer.
WITH AN EASY STROLL TO BOTANICAL GARDENS, Yarra river walking and bike trails. Be amongst the fashionable restaurants, cafes and retail outlets on Chapel street. Walk to the South Yarra train station and let's not forget Toorak Road  trams, Street Cafes and restaurants and shopping. 
The ultimate in Lifestyle and Convenience

Description:
A View for a Lifetime with Appliances Included
Bask in the northern sun as you enjoy an uninterrupted vista of Melbourne High School, the Yarra River and the city skyline. Sitting high on the 14th floor this modern apartment is fully equipped with Bosch appliances including: washing machine, dryer, dishwasher, microwave, fridge and oven. Each of the bedrooms has a BIR and master features a modern en-suite perfect for two individuals living in the apartment or guests when they visit. The open plan living room gives you different vantage point of the captivating surrounds and leads onto the generous east facing balcony.
The building has a modern foyer/ waiting area, security intercom lift access and top-notch amenities including; pool, gym, BBQ area, Outdoor deck and common area. A secure carpark and two storage units complete the picture.
The location gives you a fantastic walks score with plenty of public transport available including South Yarra station, Toorak Road and Chapel Street tram also Alexandra Ave bus. With Chapel Street and Toorak Road in such close proximity you are spoilt for choice with cafes, restaurants and retail shopping.

Description:
Forthcoming Auction
Private Inspections Now Available -Please contact Mark Konishi on 0412 825 852
Year-round entertaining has never been so appealing thanks to this stately architect designed town residence in one of South Yarras most sought-after neighbourhoods. Moments to transport, Prahran Market, Chapel Street, Fawkner Park and LHotel Gitan amongst other popular restaurants, it is also close to Albert Park Lake with easy access to the CBD and Port Philip Bay. Spanning two sensational levels, this superbly appointed home offers plenty of space for gatherings whilst providing the ultimate sanctuary away from the world outside. The substantial living zones deliver impressive flexibility with a home office, gourmet kitchen with breakfast bar, walk in pantry, granite benchtop plus premium appliances including an integrated dishwasher and an open plan living and dining precinct flowing via bi-fold doors to the private paved rear courtyard. Upstairs hosts a master suite with built in robes and a generous ensuite with twin basins and an oversized shower, a sun-filled second bedroom also with built in robes plus a luxe bathroom with shower over bath. Among the many highlights are an additional side courtyard providing a private leafy north facing aspect, zoned ducted heating/cooling throughout plus split system in each bedroom, powder room, European laundry, abundant storage and off street parking.

One-On-One Private Inspections are available for this property at a time to best suit you and your schedule.

This is the townhouse you have been looking for. Only minutes walk to bustling Chapel street and The Prahran Market, yet tucked away in a private, quiet street in exclusive South Yarra. A leafy park only metres from your door.
The Abode:
Imposing facade. Generous private, north facing courtyard. This two story townhouse has everything you could desire and more.
Downstairs living is open plan. The kitchen/living/dining opens onto a large, private, leafy north facing courtyard.
Upstairs includes a large landing, two bright and spacious bedrooms with ample storage and a large central bathroom.
The Features:
* Balcony off master bedroom
* Under floor heating
* Reverse cycle air conditioning downstairs and in both bedrooms.
* Private off street parking
* Downstairs powder room
* Downstairs courtyard
* European laundry
* North facing courtyard
The Nearby:
Cafes, restaurants, train and trams. Prahran Market. Botanical Gardens. MCG and Tennis Centre.
What to do:
Call, reach out, email but be quick as this is in high demand. Book an appointment!

Description:
Victorian Elegance, Contemporary Style - No Inspections - Contact David Volpato 0414 701 983 / Abby Innes 0423 210 790
For Sale by Expressions of Interest, Unless Sold Prior
This classic balconied Victorian residence's generous dimensions display an irresistible combination of original elegance and inspired contemporary style. Delivering enviable lifestyle appeal walking distance to Hawksburn Village and Station, Chapel Street and Toorak Road shops, Como Park and Prahran Market. A traditional arched hallway with wide American oak floors flow through to a gorgeous study/sitting room with marble open fire and a sensational expansive living and dining room warmed by a gas fireplace. Bathed in western light, a well appointed kitchen and casual dining opens to the private west-facing landscaped garden with large entertaining deck featuring banqueted seating and a retractable sun-awning.
Upstairs, a gorgeous main bedroom with balcony, built in robe, open fireplace and double glazing is completed with two additional bedrooms with built in robes and a designer bathroom. A private lifestyle oasis, it also includes hydronic heating throughout, 2nd bathroom, Euro-laundry and pedestrian right of way to Cassell Street with ample unrestricted parking.

Description:
Spectacular style, unbeatable lifestyle
One of only nine crafted by Jolson Architecture and Orchard Piper, this luxurious apartment is highlighted by a generosity of scale and superb versatility. Showcasing unparalleled style, this first floor apartment immediately establishes a serene and inviting ambience with tree top vistas and north/west light. A wide entrance featuring exquisite oak floors introduces the sophisticated interiors boasting an expansive open plan living and dining zone with floor to ceiling glass sliders creating a seamless indoor outdoor connection. The sleek kitchen is appointed with stone benches and a suite of Miele appliances plus butler's pantry complete with European laundry. The oversized main bedroom with robes and lavish ensuite is complemented by a separate flexible second bedroom with robes. Luxury appointments include gas fireplace, integrated cooling, two car spaces and storage cage. Situated moments from Toorak Road shopping, Prahran Market, Fawkner Park, Royal Botanic Gardens and multiple transport options.

South Yarras newest luxury boutique living has arrived. This contemporary apartment building has been designed and built with no expense spared and the skill set of Carrabot Holt Architects set in superb surroundings by Jack Merlo. Quiet and exclusive area within walking distance to South Yarra train station, private schools, parks, restaurants and shops. An ultra stylish and desirably low maintenance top floor apartment in a boutique block of just 6, this surprisingly private and peaceful residence offers a life of unquestionable quality and convenience. Retaining classic period character whilst boasting a glamorous renovation, it features a combined lounge and dining area with open fire place opening out to a sunny balcony, a gourmet kitchen with five burner gas stove, Caesarstone benchtops and laundry facilities, an enormous master bedroom basking in sunlight with built in robes, a well proportioned second bedroom also with built in robes plus a stunning bathroom with floor to ceiling tiling and shower over bath. Highlights of the property include split system air conditioning, timber flooring throughout, storage room, Lpermits for street parking and a communal garden. Ideal for the professional or investor seeking an opportunity to enter this highly prized community just a few minutes walk to transport, Hawksburn Village, Prahran Market and Chapel Street.

LUXURIOUS SOUTH YARRA LIVING ON THE YARRA RIVER
POSITIONED IN THE PROMINENT LANDMARK COMPLEX  "AVENUE". This sophisticated apartment offers contemporary living at its finest, showcasing designer open plan living. Superb Hecker Guthrie designed interiors wrapped in floor to ceiling windows throughout. This immaculate 1 bedroom apartment has an amazing floor plan and offers an exciting lifestyle. 
PLENTY OF NATURAL LIGHT streaming into your new home 
Intelligently designed, the open plan living and dining zone has custom designed hidden work space and plenty of storage.
The kitchen is meticulous with mirror splash backs, Smeg appliances, beautiful stone bench tops and abundance of integrated storage.
Spacious Bedroom with  mirrored built-in-robes
Luxurious bathroom with floor to ceiling tiles, beautiful rose gold taps and custom made storage.
Step onto the elegant glass-walled winter garden/ sunroom with views towards Chapel street.
WELCOME EXTRAS include secure undercover car space, hidden European laundry, timber floors in kitchen, high ceilings, heating and cooling and video intercom security. 
EMBRACING INNER CITY LIFESTYLE  this modern apartment enjoys a coveted South Yarra address. Enjoy walking everywhere with just moments from your doorstep you will find shopping precincts, cafes, dining and entertainment precincts, Yarra River, Royal Botanical Gardens and most notable Toorak Rd and Chapel St, as well as public transport which is easily accessible just minutes away.

Description:
218sqm (APPROX.) OF RARE PRIME SOUTH YARRA LAND IN ONE OF THE AREAS MOST SOUGHT AFTER STREETS - WITH FULLY ENDORSED PLANS AND PERMITS.
Featuring Approved plans for a breathtaking luxury 4 level home to rival the best. Designed by renowned Architect Robert Buckerfield to maximise the block and take advantage of the orientation.
With all the hard work and preliminaries complete, this superbly positioned site affords the astute buyer an opportunity to fast track the development and construction process and reap the rewards with minimal fuss. The property offers complete flexibility to undertake the existing scheme or to start with a blank canvass of flat land. With outstanding geography and incredible amenity the location benefits from easy access to the Toorak Road, Chapel Street and only minutes from the Schools and Hospitals are also within easy access.
This is a truly special opportunity to secure a beautiful site just minutes from the heart of Melbourne. The approved home features 3 bedroom accommodation with a multitude of formal and informal living areas. A well-crafted aesthetic will hold wide appeal and compliments the enormously practical functionality. Excellent car parking is incorporated into the property. Scope exists to vary the plan and possibly create or even look at a higher density unit development within the building envelope (Subject to Council Approval)
